name: Nebula
description:
"In a sea of chaos, only one thing moves. A cloud of gas, caught in an ancient light wind. 'The Empyrean' is the name given to it by those who study such heavenly bodies - it means 'the place where heaven meets the earth.' " - Sykcolo / AI

Nebula by @Sykcoloart

Taking something that most would consider ugly or repulsive and showing it in a different way that transforms it into something uniquely beautiful is the main passion behind this project that I called Metamorphoses.

This artwork is created using generative techniques to mutate and deconstruct a micrograph of a piece of cockroach shell. 

Learn about the inspiration, story and techniques behind this project on my website: https://www.sykcolo.com/blog-1/the-metamorphoses-collection
